data.description: If you are looking for the peaceful, quiet life but still want to be close to amenities, this beautiful country estate is for you! This 3000+ square ft. home is built with Polysteel construction to withstand nearly anything nature can throw at it and provides excellent insulating properties for superb energy efficiency. The home is currently five bedrooms, but the upstairs area can easily be reconfigured into exercise, media, or recreational spaces. This home features spacious common areas, large bedrooms, huge amounts of closet space, and ample laundry room. Outside the home are nearly 2 well-kept acres with a pristine pool and deck to enjoy, large workshop, and shelter that would be perfect for equipment, boat or RV. Make this beautiful country estate yours today!
